N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 209.2 - Application

State Regulations

This regulation shall govern all meetings of the members of
the MCU while the superintendent is in possession of the MCU's business and
property. To the extent that the bylaws of the MCU are inconsistent or conflict
with the Banking Law, this Part, or any action taken by the superintendent
hereunder, such bylaws are superseded and shall have no force and
effect. Notes
